    "This divide enables the model to train on the majority of the data and subsequently evaluate it on a separate set of data to gain a realistic understanding of how it will perform in a real-world scenario.",
    "As well as the division of each image into training and testing sets, Table 2 specifies the training and testing scenarios.",
    "This table divides the CKHK-22 dataset into training and testing sets.",
    "These sets are important for the development of a robust and accurate model for the detection of colorectal cancer.",
    "The models applied in this work are selected not because they are very fresh, but owing to their proven strengths concerning performance, interpretability, and clinical relevance for colorectal cancer tasks on detection and segmentation."
